"

[node name="Label2" parent="rove/HBoxContainer/Panel2/VBoxContainer" index="1" unique_id=728807213]
text = "When the battery enters hibernation due to low power, the inverter can use photovoltaic power or mains power to charge and activate the battery, without the need for manual operation."

